rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Item properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators with the domain of RDA Item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompaniedByItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is accompanied by (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item brought together with another item after being issued.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysisOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysis of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that has been examined to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has annotator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who makes manuscript annotations on an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has autographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person whose manuscript signature appears on an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binder
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has binder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who binds an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: boundWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is bound with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that has been bound within the same binding as the item being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectionRegistrar
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collection registrar
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate work such as a collection of items or works.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has collector
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryOnItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary on (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a set of explanatory or critical notes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containedInItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contained in (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a larger item of which a part is a discrete component.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containsItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contains (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is a discrete component of a larger item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiqueOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critique of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a critical evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has curator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body conceiving, aggregating, and/or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has current owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body currently having legal possession of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodialHistoryOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodial history of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a record of previous ownership or custodianship of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodian
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodian
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal custody of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicateeOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dedicatee of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body to whom an item is dedicated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: depositor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has depositor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a current owner of an item who deposited the item into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descriptionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is description of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item described by a describing entity.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransferOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digital transfer of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item transferred from one digital format to another.

rdf:Description.reg:name: donor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has donor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a former owner of an item who donated that item to another owner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: electronicReproductionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is electronic reproduction of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an analog item used as the basis for an electronic reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equivalentItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is equivalent item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item embodying the same expression of a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluationOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluation of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is examined or judged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: facsimileOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is facsimile of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for an exact reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmedWithItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is filmed with (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same microform with the item being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formerOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has former owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body formerly having legal possession of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honoureeOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has honouree of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body honoured by an item, e.g., a person to whom a copy is presented.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForTheItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a character string associated with an item that serves to differentiate that item from other items.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illuminator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has illuminator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person providing decoration to a specific item using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs.

rdf:Description.reg:name: immediateSourceOfAcquisitionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has immediate source of acquisition of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to the source from which the agency directly acquired an item and the circumstances under which it was received.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inscriber
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inscriber
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who has written a statement of dedication or gift on an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: itemSpecificCarrierCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has item-specific carrier characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a characteristic that applies to the carrier or carriers of the specific item being described and is assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: itemSpecificCarrierCharacteristicOfEarlyPrintedResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has item-specific carrier characteristic of early printed resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a characteristic that applies to the carrier or carriers of the specific early printed item being described and is assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation. includes rubrication, illumination, and other hand colouring, manuscript additions, and binding.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manifestationExemplified
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manifestation exemplified
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to the manifestation exemplified by an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnDimensionsOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on dimensions of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on the dimensions of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the dimensions element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnExtentOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on extent of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on the extent of a manifestation that is not recorded as part of the extent element.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnManifestationOrItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on manifestation or item of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an annotation providing additional information about manifestation or item attributes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onDiscWithItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is on disc with (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same disc with the item being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherPFCItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other person, family, or corporate body associated with an item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body other than an owner or custodian associated with an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: owner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal possession of an item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: preservationFacsimileOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is preservation facsimile of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.

rdf:Description.reg:name: relatedItemOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related item of item
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item, represented by an identifier or a description, that is related to the resource being described (e.g., an item used as the basis for a microform reproduction).

rdf:Description.reg:name: reprintOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reprint of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for a reprint with the same content as the resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reproductionOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reproduction of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a reproduction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restorationist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has restorationist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of an item by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restrictionsOnAccess
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has restrictions on access
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to limitations placed on access to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restrictionsOnUse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has restrictions on use
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to limitations placed on uses such as reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewOfItem
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is review of (item)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a brief evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: seller
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has seller
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an item to a former owner of an item who sold that item to another owner.
